# Git / editor / workspace
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.github
**/.claude
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store

# Secrets and local env (pass at runtime via -e or --env-file)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Python build artefacts / venv / caches
**/.venv
**/venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/build
**/dist
**/*.egg-info

# Node / Next.js build artefacts
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/out
**/.pnpm-store
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/pnpm-debug.log*
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Test / coverage
**/.coverage
**/coverage.xml
**/htmlcov

# Repo-level docs / notes
docs/
process-notes.md

# Misc
**/*.log
**/tmp
**/.tmp
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
